datasetName: 1970 -1975 Lundy Field Society The Marine Fauna of Lundy Pycnogonida
occurrenceRemarks: The list is based on collections and the records of Harvey (1950). Collections took place during the summer months of 1970, 1971, 1972, 1974 and 1975, occasionally by shore collecting but more frequently by diving. In both the littoral and sublittoral zones the undersurface of rocks were examined and scrapings of hydroids and bryozoa taken from all surfaces.
